# Movie Recommendations
A learning machine learning project that creates a model and recommendations from the LightFM movielens dataset.

## Resources
Many thanks to [Siraj](https://twitter.com/sirajraval?lang=en) for the incredible [videos](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gBC9R-msAk&index=3&list=PL2-dafEMk2A6QKz1mrk1uIGfHkC1zZ6UU)!

## Example

### Run Command
`./movie_recommendations.py --users 3,24`

### Output
```
User 3
     Known positives:
         Seven (Se7en) (1995)
         Contact (1997)
         Starship Troopers (1997)
     Recommended:
         Chasing Amy (1997)
         Titanic (1997)
         Boogie Nights (1997)
User 24
     Known positives:
         Toy Story (1995)
         Twelve Monkeys (1995)
         Babe (1995)
     Recommended:
         Star Wars (1977)
         Raiders of the Lost Ark (1981)
         Return of the Jedi (1983)
```

